      "dct:title": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Marine Landscape WMS"
      },
      "dct:description": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "The map service features wide variety of land forms and landscapes on the sea floor. Marine landscape is defined as a larger geographical area with visually uniform character. The interpretation is based on low-resolution depth data and parameters that can be extracted directly from these. The classification performed here is based on Naturtyper i Norge (NiN)."
      },
